OL,3,CHealth boss condemns acts of racial
OL,4,Cabuse aimed at NHS workers
OL,6,FA health leader on Teesside has
OL,7,Fwritten to staff to condemn acts of
OL,8,Fracial abuse aimed at NHS workers.
OL,10,FStacey Hunter, CEO for University
OL,11,FHospitals Tees, sent the letter to
OL,12,F16,000 staff across the organisation
OL,13,Fwhich includes the North Tees and
OL,14,FHartlepool, and South Tees Hospitals
OL,15,FTrusts.
OL,17,FIt comes after what she says have been
OL,18,F"serious incidents" and colleagues
OL,19,Fsuffering "heightened racial abuse in
OL,20,Frecent days."JMs Hunter also offered
OL,21,Fher support to those affected.
