OL,3,CHealth boss condemns acts of racial
OL,4,Cabuse aimed at NHS workers
OL,6,FIn a letter she wrote: "I want to
OL,7,Fhighlight serious incidents I was made
OL,8,Faware of today relating to a number of
OL,9,Four colleagues who have suffered
OL,10,Fheightened racial abuse in recent days.
OL,12,F"These separate incidents, in this
OL,13,Finstance happened as they travelled in
OL,14,Fto work ` are, I have no doubt, not
OL,15,Fisolated occurrences. These appalling
OL,16,Fevents are extremely worrying, and we
OL,17,Fwill not tolerate this type of abuse
OL,18,Fat any level.
