OL,6,F"We are of course working with these
OL,7,Fcolleagues to offer all of the support
OL,8,Fthey need."
OL,10,FShe continued: "I also want to offer
OL,11,Fmy absolute support to any member of
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals Tees who has
OL,13,Fsuffered similar abuse during their
OL,14,Fday-to-day lives."
