OL,3,CHealth boss condemns acts of racial
OL,4,Cabuse aimed at NHS workers
OL,6,FChief people officer for the
OL,7,Forganisation, Rachael Metcalf, added:
OL,8,F"Around 16% of our staff are from a
OL,9,Fglobal majority background. It is our
OL,10,Finclusivity that helps us to be more
OL,11,Fproductive, more efficient and
OL,12,Fimportantly helps us to keep our
OL,13,Fpatients and communities safe."
OL,15,FMs Hunter is said to be working with
OL,16,FCleveland Police and local MPs to
OL,17,Ftackle the issue.
