OL,3,CHealth boss condemns acts of racial
OL,4,Cabuse aimed at NHS workers
OL,6,F"It's important we work with all of
OL,7,Four partners over ignorance of any
OL,8,Ftype" Ms Hunter said. "I mentioned
OL,9,Fthis just this morning during a
OL,10,Fmeeting with one our local MPs who
OL,11,Fwholeheartedly agreed.
OL,13,F"I want to assure colleagues you are
OL,14,Fnot alone. Incidents like this should
OL,15,Fnever be ignored and accepted. I
OL,16,Fencourage you to please report them.
OL,17,FWe are richer for the diversity of our
OL,18,Fworkplace and our population. It's one
OL,19,Fof many things that makes the NHS so
OL,20,Fgreat."
